Let's avoid renaming packages into `metals`. By convention in this codebase, we there are two namespaces with conflicting names like `scala.meta.Position` and `org.eclipse.lsp4j.Position` then we use single character renames

```scala
import scala.{meta => m}
import org.eclipse.{lsp4j => l}
// m.Position
// l.Position
```
